:: Test J {"position":"975,5550","size":"100,100"}
{=

(metadata: "title", "Test J (NPCs)")

[[⇦ BACK->Pre-Test (NEW)]]

<ul>
''Know Test:''
<li>Veh-Veh is currently (if: $char's VehVeh's know is false)[(color:red)[unknown to you.]](else:)[(color:green)[acquainted.]]
<li>(link-rerun: "Get to know Veh-Veh.")[($funcNPCKnow: "VehVeh", "You've met Veh-Veh under the strangest of circumstances. (Custom test log)")]
</ul>

<ul>
''Arc Test:''
<li>Veh-Veh's current arc is: ''(print: $char's VehVeh's arc)''. <br> $cssDesc[Her arc conditions are: (verbatim-print: (passage: "npc.VehVeh")'s arcConditions)]
<li>Now, what if... (link-rerun: "I've left Apesai")[(set: $place's location to "Rokhab")]? And then I (link-rerun: "come back")[(set: $place's location to "Apesai")]? Or I (link-rerun: "gain a bunch of money")[($funcGainLoss: "item.", "rial", 1000)]? Or I unfortunately  (link-rerun: "lose all my money")[(if: $char's player's inv contains "rial")[(move: $char's player's inv's rial into _trash)]]?
<li>(link-rerun: "Update all NPC arcs.")[($funcUpdateNPCArc:)(redirect: (passage:)'s name)]
</ul>

<ul>
''Travel Test:''
<li>Veh-Veh's current travel mode is ''(print: $char's VehVeh's travelMode)''. <br> Her current phase is ''(print: $char's VehVeh's travel's 1st)'', making her location ''(print: $char's VehVeh's location)''. <br> She has (plural: $char's VehVeh's travel's 2nd ,"day") left before moving on.
<br> Switch Veh-Veh's intinerary ("travelMode"):
<li>... to (link-rerun: "test mode")[(set: $char's VehVeh's travelMode to "testMode")(redirect: (passage:)'s name)] ... or (link-rerun: "fresh")[(set: $char's VehVeh's travelMode to "fresh")(redirect: (passage:)'s name)].
<li>(link-rerun: "Update travel")[($funcAdvanceNPCTravel:)(redirect: (passage:)'s name)]
</ul>

<ul>
''Opinion Test:''
<li>Veh-Veh: ($funcOpinionCalc: "VehVeh", true)
<li>Your teacher: ($funcOpinionCalc: "Teacher", true)
<br>
<li>(link-rerun: "Give self 2 repDavehmarGood.")[($funcGainLoss: "att.", "repDavehmarGood", 2)]
<li>(link-rerun: "Give self 2 repDavehmarBad.")[($funcGainLoss: "att.", "repDavehmarBad", 2)]
<li>(link-rerun: "Flatter your teacher (gain 5 base opinion)")[($funcOpinionGainLoss: "Teacher", 5, "He really likes flattery.")]
<li>(link-rerun: "Piss off your teacher (lose 3 base opinion)")[($funcOpinionGainLoss: "Teacher", -3, "You pissed him off.")]
<br>
<li>(link-rerun:"Update all NPCs.")[($funcUpdateNPC:)(redirect: (passage:)'s name)] 
</ul>

<details open>
<summary>NPC list:</summary>
(box: "X", 10)[
(for: each _char,...(data-names: $char))[\
	(if: _char is not "player")[\
    	(set: _charDM to (passage: "npc."+_char))
        ''(print: _charDM's id)'' <br> (print: _charDM's desc) <br> (print: $char's _char)\
        <br>
    ]\
]]
</details>